 cards=''.join(f'<a class="service-card photo-service" href="/services/{s[0]}"><img src="{photos[s[2]]}" alt="Electrical photo for {s[1]}"><h3>{s[1]}</h3><p>Planning notes for {s[3]} around Galena, Pittsburg, and nearby communities.</p><span>Open service page →</span></a>' for s in services)
 body=f'<section class="hero circuit-shell"><div class="hero-copy"><p class="eyebrow">⚡ Galena-based electrical contractor</p><h1>Power work that feels planned before a wire gets touched.</h1><p class="hero-lede">JAG Electric handles residential and commercial electrical work around Galena, Pittsburg, and nearby communities — panel upgrades, rewiring, fixtures, outlets, remodel wiring, and clean troubleshooting.</p><div class="hero-actions"><a class="btn primary" href="tel:{tel}">Call {phone}</a><a class="btn ghost" href="/estimate-prep">Build an estimate-prep summary →</a></div><div class="proof-strip"><span>★ 4.9 Google rating / 50 reviews supplied</span><span>✓ BBB A+ / Accredited since 2020</span><span>✓ Free estimates listed on HomeAdvisor</span></div></div><div class="circuit-board" aria-label="Animated circuit-board hero graphic"><div class="trace t1"></div><div class="trace t2"></div><div class="trace t3"></div><div class="trace t4"></div><div class="pulse-ring"></div><div class="panel-card main-breaker"><small>MAIN SERVICE</small><strong>JAG</strong><em>panel · branch circuits · fixtures</em></div><span class="node node-0">Panel</span><span class="node node-1">Rewire</span><span class="node node-2">Lighting</span><span class="node node-3">Outlets</span><span class="node node-4">Remodel</span><span class="node node-5">Commercial</span></div></section>'
 body+=f'<section class="split-section"><div><p class="eyebrow">Local electrical scope</p><h2>Electrical work feels better when the scope is clear before the visit.</h2><p>JAG Electric’s public listings point to residential and commercial electrical contractor work, panel upgrades, lighting, outlet repairs, computer cable installation, and wiring for remodels and new construction. This page gives homeowners, landlords, builders, and small businesses enough context to make the first call useful.</p><p>The photo system now uses JAG public/business-profile assets plus U.S.-documented representative electrical panel photos from Wikimedia Commons. The circuit-board hero stays intact, while the body of the site carries the real electrical texture a contractor site needs.</p><p>Visitors can move from the homepage into detailed service pages, service-area pages, review proof, and an honest estimate-prep workflow. A homeowner in Pittsburg, a landlord in Galena, or a small business near Joplin should find practical next steps instead of a thin slogan and a phone number only.</p></div><div class="prep-console"><h3>Fast call checklist</h3><p class="check">Address or town</p><p class="check">Residential, commercial, rental, remodel, or new work</p><p class="check">What changed before the issue started</p><p class="check">Panel/fixture/outlet photos if safe to take</p><p class="check">Best callback window</p></div></section>'
 body+=f'<section class="services-home"><p class="eyebrow">Deep service pages</p><h2>Service pages with enough substance for homeowners and search.</h2><div class="service-grid">{cards}</div></section><section class="photo-proof"><div><p class="eyebrow">Photo-backed electrical texture</p><h2>Real panels, real wiring context, honest labels.</h2><p>Verified proof includes the phone, email, Galena address, BBB A+ accreditation listing, HomeAdvisor rating/review count, Facebook recommendation signal, and Toby-supplied Google/GBP details. Visual proof uses public JAG assets plus representative U.S.-documented electrical photos — no foreign panels, no unsupported project claims.</p></div><div class="asset-rail photo-mosaic">{photo("work","JAG Electric public work photo")}{photo("uspanel","Typical U.S. breaker panel wiring context")}{photo("subpanel","U.S. residential service panel and subpanel")}{photo("fortworth","Fort Worth, Texas 1946-home panel context")}</div></section>'+estimate()+reviews()+cta()
 return header('JAG Electric | Galena & Pittsburg KS Electrician','JAG Electric is a Galena-based residential and commercial electrician serving Pittsburg and nearby areas with panel upgrades, rewiring, lighting, outlets, remodel wiring, and commercial electrical service.',body)
